Dear Sheffield City Council,
Please provide the total number of young trees planted on Sheffield's streets over the October 2017 to March 2018 planting season.
Further, please break this number down as follows:
1. The number replacing felled mature street trees;
2. The number replacing failed young trees;
3. The number replacing damaged young trees;
4. The number planted in new locations.
Do feel free to contact me should you require any clarification regarding the above.
Yours faithfully,
Nicholaus Hall
